<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 06:16:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国碧桂园计划在下周之前支付错过的优惠券</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/country-garden-says-it-aims-pay-onshore-coupons-due-thursday-by-may-13-2024-05-09/</link><description>陷入困境的中国房地产开发商碧桂园表示，无法支付周四到期的两张境内息票，但如果未能在下周结束的宽限期内支付，中债保险公司将代其支付。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 04:59:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/country-garden-says-it-aims-pay-onshore-coupons-due-thursday-by-may-13-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>阿里巴巴所在地中国特大城市杭州取消所有购房限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-megacity-hangzhou-home-alibaba-lifts-all-home-purchase-curbs-2024-05-09/</link><description>中国东部大都市杭州是中国最繁荣的城市之一，周四表示将取消所有购房限制以提振房地产市场，这引发了其他城市效仿的前景。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 04:40:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-megacity-hangzhou-home-alibaba-lifts-all-home-purchase-curbs-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平在匈牙利讨论乌克兰和基础设施问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/chinas-xi-jinping-hungary-discuss-ukraine-infrastructure-2024-05-09/</link><description>中国国家主席习近平将于周四会见匈牙利总理欧尔班维克托，乌克兰战争和基础设施项目将成为他五年来首次欧洲之行的第三站。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 04:03:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/chinas-xi-jinping-hungary-discuss-ukraine-infrastructure-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国4月原油进口量同比增长5.45%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-april-crude-oil-imports-rise-545-previous-year-2024-05-09/</link><description>周四官方数据显示，随着炼油厂为全面恢复的劳动节假期旅行季节做准备，中国四月份原油进口量较去年同期有所增加。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 03:44:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-april-crude-oil-imports-rise-545-previous-year-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国进出口恢复增长 预示需求复苏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-exports-return-growth-april-imports-beat-forecast-2024-05-09/</link><description>周四海关数据显示，中国进出口在上月收缩后于四月份恢复增长，表明国内外需求出现令人鼓舞的改善，推动了本已摇摇欲坠的经济复苏。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 03:31:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-exports-return-growth-april-imports-beat-forecast-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国贸易数据强劲，亚洲股市稳定，日元稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-09/</link><description>亚洲股市周四企稳，此前中国贸易数据强劲，表明世界第二大经济体的国内需求正在回升，而日元在连续三天下跌后企稳，因日本谈到了潜在的货币干预措施。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 02:33:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>华为新款 Pura 70 智能手机有什么</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/what-is-huaweis-new-pura-70-smartphones-2024-05-09/</link><description>华为新款高端Pura 70智能手机系列上个月推出后迅速售空，分析师将其吹捧为苹果iPhone的又一个挑战者，并进一步表明这家中国公司正在反击美国的限制措施。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 02:05:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/what-is-huaweis-new-pura-70-smartphones-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>独家：华为新机采用更多国产零部件、存储芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/huaweis-new-phone-uses-more-china-made-parts-memory-chip-2024-05-09/</link><description>拆解分析显示，华为最新的高端手机采用了更多中国供应商，包括新的闪存存储芯片和改进的芯片处理器，这表明中国在技术自给自足方面正在取得进展。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 02:04:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/huaweis-new-phone-uses-more-china-made-parts-memory-chip-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>美国在总统就职典礼前派遣军舰通过台湾海峡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-sends-warship-through-taiwan-strait-ahead-presidential-inauguration-2024-05-09/</link><description>周三，距离台湾新总统上任不到两周，一艘美国军舰驶过狭窄的台湾海峡，引发北京的愤怒谴责。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 00:57:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-sends-warship-through-taiwan-strait-ahead-presidential-inauguration-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>美国原油库存减少导致油价上涨，中国进口量同比增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-rises-us-crude-storage-draw-fed-rate-cut-hopes-2024-05-09/</link><description>周四油价上涨，因炼油厂进口量增加以及中国上个月进口量同比增加，美国原油库存下降，支撑了全球两个最大原油消费国更高的需求预期。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 00:53:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-rises-us-crude-storage-draw-fed-rate-cut-hopes-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>美国就“伏特台风”网络间谍活动与中国对峙</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-confronts-china-over-volt-typhoon-cyber-espionage-2024-05-08/</link><description>一位美国高级网络官员表示，美国官员上个月在北京与中国政府就一场大规模的网络间谍活动进行对质，中国黑客通过该活动侵入了数十个美国关键基础设施组织。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 21:19:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-confronts-china-over-volt-typhoon-cyber-espionage-2024-05-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国批准首个基因编辑小麦，向粮食作物开放转基因技术</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-approves-first-gene-edited-wheat-step-open-up-gm-tech-food-crops-2024-05-08/</link><description>随着北京谨慎推进转基因粮食作物的商业化种植，中国首次批准了基因编辑小麦的安全性。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 16:07:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-approves-first-gene-edited-wheat-step-open-up-gm-tech-food-crops-2024-05-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国发布规则草案规范蓬勃发展的锂电池扩张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-issues-draft-rules-regulate-booming-lithium-battery-expansion-2024-05-08/</link><description>在锂电池行业的快速扩张影响了行业利润并引发了对国际市场产能过剩的担忧之后，中国于周三发布了规范其锂电池市场的规则草案。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 11:29:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-issues-draft-rules-regulate-booming-lithium-battery-expansion-2024-05-08/</guid></item><item><title>解说：壳牌出售新加坡炼油厂及其市场意义</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shells-singapore-refinery-sale-its-market-significance-2024-05-08/</link><description>石油巨头壳牌周三表示，已同意将其位于新加坡的 Bukom 炼油厂（世界上最大的炼油和贸易中心之一）出售给印度尼西亚化学品公司 PT Chandra Asri 和全球贸易公司 Glencore 的合资企业，最终完成了这一进程：去年开始。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 11:16:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shells-singapore-refinery-sale-its-market-significance-2024-05-08/</guid></item><item><title>降价后苹果3月份中国iPhone出货量反弹12%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apples-iphone-shipments-china-rebound-with-12-surge-march-after-price-cuts-2024-05-08/</link><description>中国政府下属的一家研究公司的数据显示，在该公司及其零售商降低价格后，苹果公司 3 月份在中国的 iPhone 出货量增长了 12%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 10:48:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apples-iphone-shipments-china-rebound-with-12-surge-march-after-price-cuts-2024-05-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>